  <brief_title>Prevalence of COVID-19 Infection in a Cohort of Patients Infected by the HIV and Patients Taking PrEP</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevalence of COVID-19 Infection in a Cohort of Patient Infected by the HIV and Patients Taking PrEP Pre-exposure Prophylaxis</official_title>
